rows.label: tlk70000017_04_msg0001
rows.name:
You just can't trust that
Acedia place, can you?

rows.label: tlk70000017_04_msg0002
rows.name:
It seems to wield tremendous
influence over all of the
nations in Alst...

rows.label: tlk70000017_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Besides, I can't say I put much stock
in anyone who upholds dogma, oracles,
and other such claptrap above reason.

rows.label: tlk70000017_04_msg0004
rows.name:
As a humble scientist it's
my duty to question dubious
beliefs such as those.

rows.label: tlk70000017_04_msg0005
rows.name:
There are a lot of believers in the city.
I don't think they're particularly bad
sorts, so I try to hold my tongue.
